Plugin:
    mod_qcardloader

Description:
    This plugin is designed to be used with the iPhone app Qcard. It enables
    professors to upload exercises for students to download and practice on
    their iPhones. Professors should upload the text file with both the word
    and the translation in English (IE. Bonjour/Hello) as well as the language
    file which contains the phonetics of each word.
    This site (http://www.speech.cs.cmu.edu/tools/lmtool.html) will generate a
    language file.

Prerequisites:
    N/A

Installation:
    Copy the folder 'qcardloader' into moodle/mod